1. Moja *pomisao* je bila da ostanemo kod kuće večeras. (My thought was to stay at home tonight.)
2. Kada sam čuo tu *pomisao*, shvatio sam da je to genijalno rešenje. (When I heard that thought, I realized it was a brilliant solution.)
3. Ukoliko vam se javi neka *pomisao*, nemojte je odmah odbaciti. (If a thought comes to your mind, don't dismiss it right away.)
4. Imam neku *pomisao* da će sve biti u redu. (I have a feeling that everything will be okay.)
5. Nisam siguran da je moja *pomisao* bila dobra ideja. (I'm not sure if my thought was a good idea.)
6. Svaki put kada se setim te *pomisli*, osetim se loše. (Every time I remember that thought, I feel bad.)
7. Ova *pomisao* mi se veoma dopada, mislim da ću je primeniti. (I really like this thought, I think I'll apply it.)
8. Njegova *pomisao* je bila da odustane od projekta, ali smo uspeli da ga ubedimo da nastavi. (His thought was to give up on the project, but we managed to convince him to continue.)